Simple Rails App Starter using mongoid (http://github.com/durran/mongoid).
Mostly for reference.

Mongodb setup:

# brew install mongodb
# put mongo binaries in path
## /usr/local/Cellar/mongodb/1.1.4-x86_64/bin
# start server
## mongod --dbpath /some/non/root/path
## on my system I use mongod --dbpath ~/data/db
# start mongo client and play
## mongo
## http://try.mongodb.org/

